```


1ï¸âƒ£3ï¸âƒ£ **If you accidentally committed sensitive information, how do you remove it from Git history?**
**Answer:**
âœ… Use `git filter-branch` or `git rebase` to remove it from commit history.
âœ… Force push to remote (`git push --force`), but **use with caution!**

